fd143db1-7edc-4dfc-b21f-5bb291f50b98/14281-1
01:37:32.130 --> 01:37:33.592
<v Siim Vene>Ma otsin öelda selle.</v>

fd143db1-7edc-4dfc-b21f-5bb291f50b98/14323-0
