fd143db1-7edc-4dfc-b21f-5bb291f50b98/14325-0
01:37:50.992 --> 01:37:51.352
<v Siim Vene>Et.</v>

fd143db1-7edc-4dfc-b21f-5bb291f50b98/14343-0
01:37:52.212 --> 01:37:56.098
<v Siim Vene>Aga see tähendab seda,
