fd143db1-7edc-4dfc-b21f-5bb291f50b98/14343-1
01:37:56.098 --> 01:37:57.592
<v Siim Vene>mis tähendab seda, et ee.</v>

fd143db1-7edc-4dfc-b21f-5bb291f50b98/14347-0
01:37:59.802 --> 01:38:01.562
<v Siim Vene>Kuskil seal 5. 6.</v>

fd143db1-7edc-4dfc-b21f-5bb291f50b98/14349-0
01:38:03.062 --> 01:38:03.672
<v Siim Vene>Aprillil.</v>

fd143db1-7edc-4dfc-b21f-5bb291f50b98/14358-0
01:38:04.722 --> 01:38:06.549
<v Siim Vene>5.
uuendaks aprilliks peavad olema</v>

fd143db1-7edc-4dfc-b21f-5bb291f50b98/14358-1
01:38:06.549 --> 01:38:07.592
<v Siim Vene>laboritega joon all.</v>

fd143db1-7edc-4dfc-b21f-5bb291f50b98/14369-0
01:38:08.252 --> 01:38:11.272
<v Siim Vene>Ehk siis, et kui et mingil hetkel,
