fd143db1-7edc-4dfc-b21f-5bb291f50b98/14387-1
01:38:16.380 --> 01:38:18.022
<v Siim Vene>siis eksamil ei saa lihtsalt.</v>

fd143db1-7edc-4dfc-b21f-5bb291f50b98/14396-0
01:38:19.172 --> 01:38:21.422
<v Siim Vene>Ehk siis laborid on eksamile pääsemise
