fd143db1-7edc-4dfc-b21f-5bb291f50b98/14434-3
01:38:39.633 --> 01:38:40.142
<v Siim Vene>et ee.</v>

fd143db1-7edc-4dfc-b21f-5bb291f50b98/14457-0
01:38:40.862 --> 01:38:44.695
<v Siim Vene>Et ma ei ole. Ütleme,
